  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "スターソルジャー。ハドソンの名作シューティング。キャラバン大会で有名。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A strange and evil presence is lurking in space. Crushing everything in its path, destroying spaceships full of innocent people, the brutal Starbrain is threatening the entire Galactic Empire. Starbrain, a giant computer programmed only for destruction, inhabits an enormous space station, guarded by enemy ships and robot creatures. To penetrate the station is a job for the most skillful and experienced Star Soldier - you! You'll be piloting Caesar, the fastest fighter ship in the Galactic Fleet, with an awesome arsenal of weapons at your finger-tips. Only you can end the fearsome Starbrain's spree of destruction, and restore peace to the galaxy!\n\nThe MSX version of the game was brought to the SG-1000 in Taiwan.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Computerspiel aus dem Jahr 1986",
      "lang": "de",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
    {
      "text": "1986 video game",
      "lang": "en",
